{"tid":2358785,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立法會內會通過Zoom開會適用各委員會　議員投票須開鏡頭舉手示意","createTime":"2021-01-08T11:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T11:36:46.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"184efeca27eaa1a046b1b83fed6695ee24bb337a","tid":2358785,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T11:21:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Pe_4zqX5EelN-Q9ygexrvqkzVbk=/1980x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ULQACASHJRDRNGYD633TQ5BAIU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPe_4zqX5EelN-Q9ygexrvqkzVbk%3D%2F1980x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FULQACASHJRDRNGYD633TQ5BAIU.png&h=e187b5a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n立法會內務員會今午（8日）在建制派以大多數贊成下，通過採納將Zoom視像開會擴至事務委員會、法案委員會和小組委員會正式會議。本報記者攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eyoFpKuWcxfsmWiA-y8CrQZId4c=/2732x1822/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N2OTFCT2AVA25PSLA2XJQT4TLI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeyoFpKuWcxfsmWiA-y8CrQZId4c%3D%2F2732x1822%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN2OTFCT2AVA25PSLA2XJQT4TLI.jpg&h=2d9463c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n熱血公民鄭松泰反對將Zoom視像開會擴至各大小組委員會，並關注立法會有否購買Zoom的版權，質疑日落條款非只適用於受疫情影響的會議。本報記者攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GC7sQZJqJgsbbk1DOt0rD-85igU=/1807x1204/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ASSWUYSBWFF3ZGLE4ZTD6EXKQM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGC7sQZJqJgsbbk1DOt0rD-85igU%3D%2F1807x1204%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FASSWUYSBWFF3ZGLE4ZTD6EXKQM.jpg&h=fd2c4bab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新民黨容海恩關注，日後立法會議員會否需要額外為使用Zoom而付費。本報記者攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n內會今午通過將Zoom視像開會擴至各大小組委員會，出席的立法會議員均會受《立法會《權力及特權》條例》訂明的特權和豁免權所保障。<br />\n鄭松泰關注立法會有否購買Zoom的版權外，質疑日落條款非只適用於受疫情影響的會議，憂慮有關安排會擴展至日後會議，直指在「政治上不可能接受」；新民黨容海恩則關注到議員日後會否有需要為使用Zoom須付費。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/PBDO33PIOJE25M3X5YYFERFUYQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FPBDO33PIOJE25M3X5YYFERFUYQ%2F&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIQx%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=ef976226\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FPBDO33PIOJE25M3X5YYFERFUYQ%2F&h=f217ab3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/PBDO33PIOJE25M3X5YYFERFUYQ/</a>"},{"pid":"979eada1cef91c501914137c9e79cdb1f760d615","tid":2358785,"uid":376170,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T11:23:22.000Z","msg":"如果有反建制直接彈佢出zoom<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cadc9931f4d7943ddd39991876596f002aac8c3","tid":2358785,"uid":107686,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T11:23:49.000Z","msg":"戲都費是交<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f130165fc480838ac37b157202e3846d27b3de87","tid":2358785,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T11:24:25.000Z","msg":"垃圾會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06bf55508ceaad6b7dbb437cfe97902ef336c742","tid":2358785,"uid":141837,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T11:24:36.000Z","msg":"其實班議員仲有咩用, 全部都係贊成票<br />\n每年派多幾十億比佢地同佢地既OFFICE, 買下ipad咁<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" cla